{"tid":786443,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"<終於> Porduce101 第一名 「SOMI」與JYP娛樂解除合約","createTime":"2018-08-20T02:30:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-21T05:57:57.000Z","uid":88491,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"8e9611d2227a2da2618107d17877ae4d9d91230d","tid":786443,"uid":88491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T02:30:38.000Z","msg":"JYP娛樂20日在官方網頁上表示:JYP娛樂與旗下所屬藝人全昭彌在商議後解除專屬合約。<br />\n<br />\n真心感謝一直以來在一起的藝人與粉絲們。<br />\n<br />\n全昭彌在2016年時參加MNET Porduce101節目，以國民製作人的大力支持贏得第一名，以<br />\n團體I.O.I出道。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以下為JYP娛樂聲明<br />\n<br />\n大家好 這裡是JYP娛樂<br />\n<br />\nJYP娛樂與旗下所屬藝人全昭彌在經過商議之後決定解除專屬合約<br />\n<br />\n真心感謝一路一起走來的藝人與粉絲們<br />\n<br />\n謝謝大家<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.newsen.com/news_view.php?uid=201808201028360410\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.newsen.com%2Fnews_view.php%3Fuid%3D201808201028360410&d=4T8dbDUuPIXk%2FVoA3xnEsZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=a81e0c39\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.newsen.com/news_view.php?uid=201808201028360410</a><br />\nJYP方對於將要出道的新女團回應:新女團正在好好的準備中。<br />\n對於全昭彌解除專屬合約的理由，則表示:請確認公司的官方聲明，此外不會多說什麼。"},{"pid":"0d27da30305491deb08877c69f2e21eefd187768","tid":786443,"uid":88491,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T02:32:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/20/103154_a408acce648fd71290372f327cb563e3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F20%2F103154_a408acce648fd71290372f327cb563e3.png&h=cd65ec06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSomi離開JYP&hellip;「解除專屬合同」 ​​​"},{"pid":"b3011c5db9a70066beddf20f6cdac13b2c211ffc","tid":786443,"uid":104811,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T02:34:07.000Z","msg":"仲以為佢會入新女團 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c40454a29aead55809334599306160700ac4947b","tid":786443,"uid":2781,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":